OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright
OL,6,Fevening then remaining dry overnight
OL,7,Fwith long clear spells. More cloud at
OL,8,Ftimes across Shetland. Becoming rather
OL,9,Fcool overnight. Light north or
OL,10,Fnortheasterly wind.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAnother dry day with variable
OL,13,Famounts of cloud and some decent
OL,14,Fspells of sunshine. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHigh
OL,17,Fpressure will maintain the dry and
OL,18,Fsettled weather through this period.
OL,19,FRather cool and cloudy at times but
OL,20,Fsome bright spells too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
